  <Properties />
  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="1"><![CDATA[The Example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>There is a simple <strong>BindingNavigator </strong>control on the <em>Form </em>but with custom images set for its buttons.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="1"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p><strong>BindingNavigator.Buttons</strong> property gets the toolbar buttons collection. You can modify items of this collection for instance set custom image or tooltip text for the button.</p><p>Property type: Gizmox.WebGui.Forms.ToolBarItemCollection</p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
</Data>